<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="chr.wilck;;53" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">WChr53</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τῷ ἀγ</supplied>απητῷ ἀδελφῷ καὶ η<hi rend="diaeresis">ὐ</hi>λ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>γημένῳ 

    <lb n="2"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="6.5"><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐν</supplied></lem><rdg><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/></rdg></app> τῷ θεῷ Παύλῳ 

    <lb n="3"/>Ἄπα <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>ωάννης 

    <lb n="4"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">βούλο</supplied>μαι μὲν καταξιωθῆναι ἀε<hi rend="diaeresis">ὶ</hi> γράφειν 

    <lb n="5"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τῇ σῇ</supplied> θεοσεβείᾳ καὶ προσαγορεύειν τὴν 

    <lb n="6"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="6.5"><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀνε</supplied>φάμιλλόν</lem><rdg><gap extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε</supplied>φάμιλλόν</rdg></app> σου καλοκαγαθίαν 

    <lb n="7"/><choice><corr><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀδι</supplied>αλείπτως</corr><sic><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αδι</supplied>αλιπτως</sic></choice>, μὴ φορτικὸς δὲ ὅμως γε-

    <lb n="8"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">νέσ</supplied>θαι τῇ σῇ τιμιότητι περὶ οἱουδήποτε 

    <lb n="9"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πρά</supplied>γματος, ἀλλὰ τὸ γνωστὸν τῆς πρὸς ἀλ-

    <lb n="10"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">λήλο</supplied>υς συνηθείας <choice><corr>αὐ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">τὸ</supplied></corr><sic>αυ</sic></choice> τοῦτο καὶ οὐδὲν ἕτε-

    <lb n="11"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρον</supplied> παρασκευάζει πολλοὺς εἰδότας τὸ 


    <lb n="12"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σὸν</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear>ἰς ἡμᾶς ἐνδιάθετον προσφεύ<add place="supralinear">γ</add>ειν 

    <lb n="13"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μοι</supplied> καὶ ποιῆσαι δεηθῆναί <add place="supralinear">σου</add> τῆς εὐγενείας, 

    <lb n="14"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἵνα μ</supplied>ὴ ἀμελήσῃς περὶ Μακαρίου· <hi rend="asper">ὅ</hi>σου γὰρ 

    <lb n="15"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">παρέ</supplied>χεις, <choice><corr>λήμψει</corr><sic>λημψι</sic></choice> ἐκ πλήρους. <choice><corr>γνῶθι</corr><sic>γνωθει</sic></choice> δὲ, 

    <lb n="16"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὅτι ἐ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>υπήθην διό<add place="supralinear">τι</add> ἀπεδήμησας ἀλόγως 

    <lb n="17"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="6.5"><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">εἰ μ</supplied>ὴ αὕτη</lem><rdg><gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ει</unclear> αυτη</rdg></app> ἐστὶν ἡ συνταγή, ἀλλ᾽ ἐχάρην 

    <lb n="18"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀκού</supplied>σας διὰ τοῦ πραιποσίτου, ὅτι <app type="BL"><lem resp="6.5">ἀνέρχῃ</lem><rdg>ἀπέρχῃ</rdg></app> 

    <lb n="19"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ταχ</supplied>υτέρου πρὸς ἡμᾶς. <choice><corr>Ἱέρακι</corr><sic><hi rend="diaeresis">ι</hi>εραξ</sic></choice> οὖν τῷ 

    <lb n="20"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κατα</supplied>φέροντί σοι ταῦτά μου τὰ γράμματα 

    <lb n="21"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀξί</supplied>ωσον συνβοηθῆσαι αὐτῷ εἰς ὃ ἐὰν 

    <lb n="22"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δυνα</supplied>τόν σοι τῇ τιμιότητι. προσαγορεύω 

    <lb n="23"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τὴν</supplied> σὴν διάθεσιν καὶ τὰ <subst><add place="inline">φίλτατά</add><del rend="corrected">φιλλατα</del></subst> σου τὰ 

    <lb n="24"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πάν</supplied>τα, τοῦτο γὰρ προτάτ<g type="apostrophe"/>τεσθαι εὔλογον 

    <lb n="25"/><gap extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/>δ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ό</unclear>τα περὶ τῶν αὐτῶν <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>παρχθῆναι. 

    <lb n="26"/><handShift new="m2"/> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">προσα</supplied>γορεύει δὲ τῇ σῇ διαθέσει ὁ ἀγαπητὸς <subst><add place="inline">Παπνούθης</add><del rend="corrected">ωραπνουθης</del></subst>. 

    <lb n="27"/><handShift new="m1"/> <gap desc="Coptic" extent="5" reason="ellipsis" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="meta.33624" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.33624" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="376" type="textDate">spätes  IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.33624" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Griechisch - koptisch. Gehört zum Archiv des Apa Johannes. Zum Ort und zur Datierung vgl. BL X, S. 5 und S. 85 mit BASP 32, 1995, S. 190 - 192 (Datierung gegen BL VI, S. 5).</p></div><div n="meta.33624" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Amh.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">145</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">33624</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0057</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">145</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0057;2;145" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.33624" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">5</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.33624" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Plate XXI</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.33624" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">W.Chr. 53</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Naldini, Cristianesimo 49</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.33624" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de"><head lang="de">Deutsch